1
00:01:48,074 --> 00:01:51,100
I'm Phoenix. I love the moon

2
00:01:51,144 --> 00:01:54,978
Especially when it's full
and most beautiful

3
00:01:55,014 --> 00:01:59,246
I don't know why
but my parents are never home...

4
00:02:01,521 --> 00:02:06,322
Daddy, Mommy...

5
00:02:06,359 --> 00:02:10,318
I just saw two people fly past the moon

6
00:02:11,664 --> 00:02:16,124
You must have been dreaming
People can't fly

7
00:02:17,937 --> 00:02:21,873
Too much TV for you!
What an overactive imagination!

8
00:02:21,908 --> 00:02:23,933
No. I really saw it

9
00:02:24,611 --> 00:02:26,442
Tomorrow's a school day

10
00:02:26,479 --> 00:02:29,004
How about a story to put you to sleep?

11
00:02:30,383 --> 00:02:33,978
Do you want Mommy to tell you a story
about the Emei Sect of Kung Fu

12
00:02:34,020 --> 00:02:36,784
or Daddy to tell about the 18 Coppermen?

13
00:02:36,823 --> 00:02:39,348
Mommy and Daddy are great storytellers

14
00:02:39,392 --> 00:02:44,625
Every story is about
a kung fu master with mystical powers

15
00:02:44,664 --> 00:02:48,623
Daddy's 18 Coppermen are especially cute

16
00:02:48,668 --> 00:02:54,129
Their stories are fun
but I never believed them...

17
00:02:54,174 --> 00:02:56,267
until one day when I was 14 years old...

18
00:03:07,420 --> 00:03:08,785
Daddy!

19
00:03:15,295 --> 00:03:16,387
Mommy!

20
00:04:33,273 --> 00:04:36,333
Relax, don't be scared
I've got to call the police

21
00:04:39,479 --> 00:04:41,208
Where's your parents?

22
00:04:51,124 --> 00:04:52,022
Dad!

23
00:04:52,058 --> 00:04:53,548
Don't be scared, sweetie!

24
00:05:03,936 --> 00:05:06,097
We've been searching for
you two for sometime...

25
00:05:07,273 --> 00:05:08,205
It's my turn!

26
00:06:11,604 --> 00:06:12,969
Attack me...?

27
00:06:25,585 --> 00:06:27,519
Get down! Come down I dare you!

28
00:06:48,975 --> 00:06:49,771
Dad!

29
00:06:52,678 --> 00:06:53,667
Go to hell!

30
00:06:58,885 --> 00:07:01,183
Awesome Dad! Pretty clever, Phoenix

31
00:07:01,220 --> 00:07:04,553
Mom, why do you suddenly know kung fu?

32
00:07:05,925 --> 00:07:10,021
Do you remember that you
once saw people fly past the moon?

33
00:07:10,062 --> 00:07:11,620
That was your Dad and me

34
00:07:11,664 --> 00:07:14,428
That's right. Our family has
a natural talent for kung fu

35
00:07:14,467 --> 00:07:16,162
We belong to the
Secret Society of Kung Fu Masters

36
00:07:16,202 --> 00:07:17,692
The Secret Society of Kung Fu Masters?

37
00:07:18,504 --> 00:07:20,972
The ancient and mysterious
world of kung fu

38
00:07:21,007 --> 00:07:23,976
still lives on today

39
00:07:24,010 --> 00:07:27,810
But we don't want to disturb society

40
00:07:27,847 --> 00:07:32,181
In secret, we help
the weak and eliminate evildoers

41
00:07:32,218 --> 00:07:34,345
We've been chasing
these two for a long time

42
00:07:34,387 --> 00:07:37,117
We never thought they'd pay us visit

43
00:07:38,124 --> 00:07:39,853
Can I learn martial arts too?

44
00:07:39,892 --> 00:07:41,223
Of course you can

45
00:07:41,260 --> 00:07:43,319
Once they turn 14 years old, every child

46
00:07:43,362 --> 00:07:46,195
can go to Mount Hua to study
martial arts every summer vacation!

47
00:07:46,232 --> 00:07:47,096
Really?

48
00:07:47,133 --> 00:07:49,829
Then I'll be as good as you

49
00:07:50,703 --> 00:07:52,034
You've got the talent

50
00:07:52,071 --> 00:07:54,801
One day you'll be better than us

51
00:07:54,841 --> 00:07:56,138
So when can we go?

52
00:07:57,176 --> 00:07:58,404
Why not right now?

53
00:08:09,755 --> 00:08:11,848
Mom, people are flying across the moon!

54
00:08:13,192 --> 00:08:15,888
You brats! A liar just like your father!

55
00:08:15,928 --> 00:08:18,897
I'm not lying

56
00:08:53,099 --> 00:08:54,760
This is Mount Hua

57
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:55,494
That's right!

58
00:08:55,535 --> 00:08:58,470
I've never flown so high!

59
00:09:24,764 --> 00:09:25,924
She's really cool!

60
00:09:27,300 --> 00:09:30,758
She called Rouge
She's the best kung fu student here

61
00:09:43,282 --> 00:09:44,271
Time to land

62
00:09:54,026 --> 00:09:58,588
Phoenix, this is where
we studied our martial arts

63
00:10:03,636 --> 00:10:04,603
Principal of the Academy?

64
00:10:05,838 --> 00:10:11,401
Master, you brought
your daughter this time

65
00:10:11,444 --> 00:10:15,574
This is Principal of the Academy
the headmaster of the school

66
00:10:15,615 --> 00:10:17,674
Why's he walking backwards?

67
00:10:18,451 --> 00:10:20,043
Kids say the darnedest things
Don't worry about it

68
00:10:20,086 --> 00:10:24,022
Long ago, I made a very big mistake

69
00:10:24,056 --> 00:10:26,081
I let an evil disciple escape

70
00:10:26,125 --> 00:10:30,027
I promised I would bring him to justice

71
00:10:30,062 --> 00:10:33,190
