73
00:10:34,800 --> 00:10:38,201
He's No. 1 on our Most Wanted List:
White Eyebrows!

74
00:10:38,237 --> 00:10:40,364
What'd he do wrong?

75
00:10:40,406 --> 00:10:43,898
He's committed innumerable crimes

76
00:10:43,943 --> 00:10:45,638
Theft, Murder, Rape

77
00:10:45,678 --> 00:10:47,077
He uses kung fu to hurt ordinary people

78
00:10:47,113 --> 00:10:50,082
And he stole our school's
most precious classic

79
00:10:50,116 --> 00:10:51,913
<The Classic of the Nine Negatives>

80
00:10:52,752 --> 00:10:58,691
Luckily, for 300 years
no one has deciphered its true meaning

81
00:10:58,724 --> 00:11:01,420
If he ever does, many people will die

82
00:11:01,460 --> 00:11:03,087
Nobody will be able to stop him

83
00:11:03,129 --> 00:11:04,221
Hey, Master

84
00:11:04,263 --> 00:11:06,163
Any news about White Eyebrows?

85
00:11:06,198 --> 00:11:10,191
Not yet. But one day

86
00:11:10,236 --> 00:11:12,227
I will arrest him!

87
00:11:14,273 --> 00:11:15,501
Amitabha Buddha

88
00:11:22,882 --> 00:11:26,477
Master Grand Grandiloquence
where's Principal of the Academy?

89
00:11:29,121 --> 00:11:31,282
In the back Thanks

90
00:11:33,059 --> 00:11:34,617
Principal of the Academy

91
00:11:35,895 --> 00:11:36,725
How can I help you?

92
00:11:36,762 --> 00:11:37,626
Nothing

93
00:11:37,663 --> 00:11:44,364
But... can we date when we grow up?

94
00:11:44,403 --> 00:11:47,463
You can't date me
but someone else is fine

95
00:11:47,506 --> 00:11:52,500
I mean, can I date someone
who doesn't know martial arts?

96
00:11:52,545 --> 00:11:54,035
Of course, but...

97
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:56,674
you mustn't let him know
you know martial arts

98
00:11:57,583 --> 00:11:59,414
That sounds pretty difficult

99
00:11:59,452 --> 00:12:00,612
You forget about destiny

100
00:12:00,653 --> 00:12:03,679
If the man of your destiny comes along
it's no problem

101
00:12:03,723 --> 00:12:05,315
So who's the man of my destiny?

102
00:12:06,358 --> 00:12:08,758
The man of your destiny is someone...

103
00:12:08,794 --> 00:12:13,993
who will only see you
once it's impossible to see you

104
00:12:14,033 --> 00:12:19,733
Someone who will only see me
once it's impossible to see me?

105
00:12:19,772 --> 00:12:21,740
Meditate on this

106
00:12:23,709 --> 00:12:25,404
Impossible to see me?

107
00:12:27,947 --> 00:12:29,938
That was my happiest summer vacation ever

108
00:12:29,982 --> 00:12:33,247
I learnt many kung fu techniques
I even taught the 18 Coppermen to dance

109
00:13:00,613 --> 00:13:02,638
Everybody liked me

110
00:13:02,681 --> 00:13:04,444
except one...

111
00:13:05,618 --> 00:13:09,987
I knew, one day
Rouge and I would have it out

112
00:13:20,733 --> 00:13:22,701
My watch reads 8:58 AM

113
00:13:22,735 --> 00:13:26,102
That means everybody
behind me will be late

114
00:13:38,851 --> 00:13:39,909
Miss Salina...

115
00:13:39,952 --> 00:13:42,853
That tramp Phoenix is in the far back

116
00:13:42,888 --> 00:13:43,684
Really?

117
00:13:45,424 --> 00:13:49,417
Bitch! She thinks she's so pretty
Just one minute late...

118
00:13:49,461 --> 00:13:50,450
and she's fired!

119
00:13:52,398 --> 00:13:53,626
Good morning, everyone

120
00:13:54,633 --> 00:13:59,127
Downsize! That's my first
order of business at Lam's Group

121
00:13:59,171 --> 00:14:02,732
Too much excess personnel
It's time to slim down

122
00:14:02,775 --> 00:14:07,007
Mr. Dragon is our new CEO

123
00:14:07,046 --> 00:14:10,846
His main mission is to cut costs

124
00:14:10,883 --> 00:14:15,081
