too power hungry and immoral

228
00:19:48,086 --> 00:19:51,021
I'm not one to quarrel with people

229
00:19:51,056 --> 00:19:53,786
So I'd rather not attend

230
00:19:53,825 --> 00:19:55,452
But if I don't go
I might offend the others

231
00:19:55,494 --> 00:19:57,655
So I want you to represent me

232
00:19:57,696 --> 00:20:01,757
Plus, my daughter graduated
and is returning from the USA

233
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:04,701
Family comes first. You can trust me

234
00:20:04,736 --> 00:20:05,794
Great

235
00:20:07,406 --> 00:20:11,638
You two, just a second ago...
what do you call that position?

236
00:20:19,451 --> 00:20:20,941
Mom, I'm back

237
00:20:20,986 --> 00:20:22,681
I'm in the kitchen

238
00:20:34,633 --> 00:20:36,123
Chicken with shark's fin

239
00:20:37,569 --> 00:20:38,536
That sucks!

240
00:20:38,704 --> 00:20:41,264
Phoenix, why'd you beat up Brother Wai?

241
00:20:41,306 --> 00:20:43,399
I saw a man. I thought he was a thief

242
00:20:43,442 --> 00:20:46,172
He's my client. I invited him to dinner

243
00:20:46,211 --> 00:20:48,702
Look, you practically killed him

244
00:20:48,747 --> 00:20:50,977
Nothing acupressure on
his pleasure points can't cure

245
00:20:57,289 --> 00:21:00,417
What a feeling! What a high!

246
00:21:02,728 --> 00:21:04,593
Did someone just hit me?

247
00:21:04,630 --> 00:21:05,096
No

248
00:21:05,130 --> 00:21:07,724
Just a happy hour
You got drunk and started hallucinating

249
00:21:07,766 --> 00:21:08,858
Come on... let me introduce you

250
00:21:08,900 --> 00:21:10,458
This is my daughter Phoenix

251
00:21:12,137 --> 00:21:13,832
Hello, Phoenix

252
00:21:13,872 --> 00:21:16,670
Hello! Call me Little Willy

253
00:21:16,708 --> 00:21:17,640
You that small?

254
00:21:17,676 --> 00:21:18,938
Yes Phoenix

255
00:21:18,977 --> 00:21:23,676
Brother Wai just bought a luxury car
He'll take you out for a spin

256
00:21:24,716 --> 00:21:26,445
Mom, we've got to talk

257
00:21:28,487 --> 00:21:30,114
Take your time

258
00:21:32,557 --> 00:21:34,855
Who are you introducing to me this time?

259
00:21:34,893 --> 00:21:39,296
Brother Wai's rich
I helped him buy several luxury flats

260
00:21:39,331 --> 00:21:41,822
I earned over a million
in commission alone

261
00:21:41,867 --> 00:21:44,995
Please don't set me up with more ugly men

262
00:21:45,037 --> 00:21:48,063
The handsome ones are unreliable and poor

263
00:21:48,106 --> 00:21:49,164
Look at your Dad

264
00:21:49,207 --> 00:21:51,903
A business failure. Totally unreliable

265
00:21:53,011 --> 00:21:54,137
But Dad's a kung fu master

266
00:21:54,179 --> 00:21:55,840
Is kung fu going to feed you?

