then you'll die peacefully

808
01:00:28,292 --> 01:00:30,226
This is your daughter?

809
01:00:30,260 --> 01:00:31,249
Yes...

810
01:00:31,295 --> 01:00:33,354
Rouge, say hi to Uncle White

811
01:00:34,198 --> 01:00:35,290
Hi, Uncle White

812
01:00:35,332 --> 01:00:38,699
What good fortune to have
such a beautiful daughter!

813
01:00:38,735 --> 01:00:41,727
Thank you... Let's talk over there

814
01:00:46,009 --> 01:00:48,443
Son-in-law, who is that?

815
01:00:48,478 --> 01:00:50,776
