823
01:01:13,170 --> 01:01:15,968
Too bad our project together
wasn't a success

824
01:01:16,006 --> 01:01:20,966
Business is a day's work
But friendship is for a lifetime, right?

825
01:01:21,011 --> 01:01:22,035
Honey

826
01:01:29,653 --> 01:01:31,553
I'm just giving you a hand

827
01:01:32,155 --> 01:01:33,986
Thank you Honey

828
01:01:34,024 --> 01:01:36,652
I cooked this especially for you. Eat up

829
