he would give it to an employee

842
01:02:35,786 --> 01:02:38,687
Rouge is making sure he doesn't drink

843
01:02:40,023 --> 01:02:42,651
We can't make our move today

844
01:02:42,693 --> 01:02:47,528
Come to my clubhouse tonight
for another plan

845
01:02:52,069 --> 01:02:54,663
Do you know why I stopped today?

846
01:02:56,006 --> 01:02:57,337
Why?

847
01:02:57,374 --> 01:03:03,472
Because in the crowd
there were 3 kung fu masters

848
01:03:04,348 --> 01:03:05,781
Really?

849
