858
01:03:40,317 --> 01:03:44,947
I'll ask my husband
to give you all his best assets

859
01:03:44,988 --> 01:03:46,819
just don't hurt him, OK?

860
01:03:47,624 --> 01:03:49,285
Why?

861
01:03:49,326 --> 01:03:52,386
You're only after
old bastard's money, right?

862
01:03:52,429 --> 01:03:55,330
