Rouge and your husband myself?

866
01:04:05,475 --> 01:04:07,943
But Rouge is your daughter

867
01:04:07,978 --> 01:04:11,709
You disobey me? I'll kill you too!

868
01:04:11,748 --> 01:04:16,378
If I don't hear he's dead tomorrow

869
01:04:16,420 --> 01:04:20,914
your daughter will disappear
from this world!

870
01:04:22,859 --> 01:04:23,985
Get down!

871
01:04:53,690 --> 01:04:54,884
Are you OK?

872
01:05:01,932 --> 01:05:05,766
White Eyebrows? I knew you looked familiar

873
01:05:13,877 --> 01:05:15,538
