876
01:05:23,687 --> 01:05:24,949
You bastard!

877
01:05:47,677 --> 01:05:48,166
Sweetie

878
01:05:48,211 --> 01:05:51,203
Get out of here with Dragon
Don't wait for me

879
01:05:51,248 --> 01:05:52,943
Itchiban, you too

880
01:05:57,287 --> 01:05:58,379
Hello

881
01:05:58,421 --> 01:05:59,683
Brother, you looking for me?

882
01:05:59,723 --> 01:06:00,519
Where are you?

883
01:06:01,458 --> 01:06:03,926
I'm already in a taxi
Don't worry about me

884
01:06:04,561 --> 01:06:06,153
I'm so relieved

885
01:06:07,631 --> 01:06:08,529
Dad!

886
01:06:16,806 --> 01:06:17,670
Big Bird!

887
01:06:43,166 --> 01:06:45,464
Dragon, are you OK? Dragon

888
01:06:46,670 --> 01:06:47,466
I...

889
