891
01:06:53,643 --> 01:06:57,079
Hawk can take him to Mount Hua
Find Principal of the Academy

892
01:06:57,113 --> 01:06:59,274
He'll think of a way to save him

893
01:06:59,316 --> 01:07:02,183
