to carry all three of us

894
01:07:02,219 --> 01:07:05,882
You two go first!
I'll figure out a way to get there

895
01:07:05,922 --> 01:07:07,150
If he gets any worse

896
01:07:07,190 --> 01:07:10,250
you impart the strength
from your martial arts to save him

897
01:07:12,796 --> 01:07:14,491
Where to? Mount Hua

898
01:07:18,168 --> 01:07:20,295
Hold on, we're almost to Mount Hua

899
01:07:21,438 --> 01:07:26,535
