900
01:07:26,576 --> 01:07:29,841
Don't talk nonsense!
Hawk is flying there now

901
01:07:30,814 --> 01:07:34,181
I think we're going the wrong way

902
01:07:34,217 --> 01:07:35,115
Why?

903
01:07:36,886 --> 01:07:38,444
Look over there

904
01:07:45,528 --> 01:07:46,893
Hawk, where are you going?

905
01:07:46,930 --> 01:07:49,524
We want to go to Mount Hua
not Mount Fuji!

906
01:07:49,566 --> 01:07:50,897
You dumb beast

907
01:07:57,607 --> 01:07:58,471
You pervert

908
01:07:58,508 --> 01:08:00,408
You're a hawk
Why are you chasing a crane?

909
01:08:00,443 --> 01:08:03,310
Now we have to spend the night here

910
01:08:10,086 --> 01:08:12,145
Don't scold him

911
01:08:13,623 --> 01:08:15,784
It's fate

912
01:08:15,825 --> 01:08:20,319
If I'm going to die, nothing can save me

913
01:08:21,398 --> 01:08:25,027
No. I won't let you die. You can't die

914
01:08:28,338 --> 01:08:30,067
Why do you treat me so well?

915
01:08:31,374 --> 01:08:35,174
Because you're the man of my destiny

916
01:08:37,981 --> 01:08:39,846
You know...

917
01:08:41,785 --> 01:08:48,349
in the beginning, I was afraid of you

918
01:08:48,391 --> 01:08:51,155
And... tried to avoid you

919
01:08:56,533 --> 01:08:57,795
And then?

920
01:09:02,639 --> 01:09:04,402
Then fear turned into love

921
01:09:47,684 --> 01:09:50,016
Cabbie, how much?

922
01:09:50,053 --> 01:09:51,486
$88,000

923
01:09:51,521 --> 01:09:53,079
Wow. It would have been cheaper to fly!

924
01:09:53,123 --> 01:09:54,886
I don't know how to go back!

925
01:09:54,924 --> 01:09:57,984
Alright... Can I pay by credit card?

926
01:09:59,028 --> 01:10:00,188
