928
01:10:02,532 --> 01:10:04,966
He'll die within an hour

929
01:10:05,001 --> 01:10:06,093
What can we do?

930
01:10:06,136 --> 01:10:07,296
We still have one last chance

931
01:10:07,337 --> 01:10:07,894
What is it?

932
01:10:07,937 --> 01:10:09,302
Use a Buddhist medicine...

933
01:10:09,339 --> 01:10:12,308
called The Cruel Cure
to bring him back from the dead

934
01:10:12,342 --> 01:10:15,607
It will also impart
30 years of kung fu training

935
01:10:15,645 --> 01:10:16,634
What are you waiting for?

936
01:10:16,679 --> 01:10:19,011
However, after swallowing that pill

937
01:10:19,048 --> 01:10:21,346
he will forget everyone he has loved

938
01:10:21,384 --> 01:10:23,944
Even the woman he loves most...

939
01:10:23,987 --> 01:10:26,387
will seem like a hag
at the supermarket to him

940
01:10:26,423 --> 01:10:27,822
No feeling what so ever

941
01:10:27,857 --> 01:10:30,382
Dad, there's got to be another way

942
01:10:30,427 --> 01:10:32,088
Sweetie, save him first

943
01:10:32,128 --> 01:10:33,959
Life comes before love

944
01:10:58,955 --> 01:11:02,015
We've survived so many dangers together

945
01:11:02,058 --> 01:11:04,083
Just when our relationship is starting

946
01:11:05,762 --> 01:11:07,889
why must I feed you this pill...

947
01:11:07,931 --> 01:11:10,422
that will make you forget me?

948
01:11:12,535 --> 01:11:14,526
Is God testing us?

949
01:11:18,641 --> 01:11:22,372
Wait any longer and it'll be too late

950
01:11:50,807 --> 01:11:55,073
Phoenix, this isn't love

951
01:12:05,922 --> 01:12:08,857
We're two people from two different worlds

952
01:12:35,652 --> 01:12:39,645
Dragon, I trust you

953
01:12:41,391 --> 01:12:43,188
I know you won't forget me

954
01:13:00,944 --> 01:13:02,434
Dragon, are you OK?

955
01:13:05,448 --> 01:13:06,779
I'm OK

956
01:13:07,584 --> 01:13:09,484
But Ms., who are you?

957
01:13:10,553 --> 01:13:12,316
Why are you sleeping next to me?

958
01:13:14,958 --> 01:13:16,152
I...

959
01:13:17,060 --> 01:13:19,119
She's the woman you love most

960
01:13:21,064 --> 01:13:23,794
I know you. You were my bodyguard

961
01:13:24,801 --> 01:13:27,497
Not only that
I loaned you a couple million

962
01:13:27,537 --> 01:13:29,027
You old cheat

963
01:13:33,276 --> 01:13:34,573
But...

964
01:13:35,979 --> 01:13:37,970
Ms., you look very familiar

965
01:13:40,583 --> 01:13:42,813
But I can't recall who you are

966
01:13:50,426 --> 01:13:51,950
White Eyebrows has learned
the 9th Negative

967
01:13:51,995 --> 01:13:53,986
he is simply too powerful

968
01:13:54,030 --> 01:13:56,157
We can't beat him

969
01:13:56,766 --> 01:13:57,824
Then...

970
01:13:57,867 --> 01:14:01,803
We have to use
our sect's strongest technique

971
01:14:01,838 --> 01:14:05,899
Unfortunately, nobody
has ever successfully learned it

972
01:14:05,942 --> 01:14:08,536
<The Technique of the Pure
and Lethal Heart>?

973
01:14:08,578 --> 01:14:10,478
Sure. 4 people must practise it together

974
01:14:10,513 --> 01:14:12,037
2 men and 2 women are best

975
01:14:12,081 --> 01:14:13,878
They must be two couples in love

976
01:14:13,916 --> 01:14:15,349
And they must practise it together

977
01:14:15,385 --> 01:14:16,852
Once learned... it is truly awesome

978
01:14:16,886 --> 01:14:19,980
The force of 4 people equals 100

979
01:14:20,857 --> 01:14:22,188
But where can we find 4 people?

980
01:14:27,230 --> 01:14:30,393
Hello, Dolina

981
01:14:31,934 --> 01:14:34,494
So sorry, Brother Wai

982
01:14:34,537 --> 01:14:37,995
My daughter's no where to be found

983
01:14:38,041 --> 01:14:39,702
I don't mind

984
01:14:39,742 --> 01:14:42,734
Dinner tonight is still great...

985
01:14:42,779 --> 01:14:44,144
so long as you're here

986
01:14:44,180 --> 01:14:45,272
Me?

987
01:14:45,314 --> 01:14:48,750
Honestly, I've been thinking...

988
01:14:48,785 --> 01:14:52,084
We're a better match than
me and your daughter

989
01:14:52,121 --> 01:14:53,986
How about... being my girlfriend?

990
01:14:54,023 --> 01:14:55,650
You psycho

991
01:14:55,692 --> 01:14:58,957
