so he goes for the mom

992
01:14:58,995 --> 01:15:00,826
He moves fast, doesn't he?

993
01:15:00,863 --> 01:15:04,663
I've considered it thoroughly
You understand me

994
01:15:04,701 --> 01:15:10,105
You care for me. You love me

995
01:15:10,139 --> 01:15:11,936
I can feel it

996
01:15:12,508 --> 01:15:14,373
I care for your money!

997
01:15:14,410 --> 01:15:15,240
Be my girlfriend

998
01:15:16,679 --> 01:15:18,442
Piss off!

999
01:15:18,481 --> 01:15:20,745
If I'm not careful
I just might beat you to death

1000
01:15:22,218 --> 01:15:23,776
Brother Wai, excuse me...

1001
01:15:23,820 --> 01:15:24,912
Mom

1002
01:15:26,255 --> 01:15:28,120
What are you here for?

1003
01:15:28,157 --> 01:15:29,818
