1009
01:15:59,922 --> 01:16:00,786
Stop!

1010
01:16:03,826 --> 01:16:05,384
Can you stop hitting each other?

1011
01:16:05,428 --> 01:16:09,387
They're not hitting each other
they're hitting me

1012
01:16:10,299 --> 01:16:11,789
