fart it out already

1013
01:16:14,437 --> 01:16:17,065
Principal of the Academy has given us
the Lethal Heart technique

1014
01:16:17,106 --> 01:16:20,439
Only 2 pairs of family members
or devoted lovers...

1015
01:16:20,476 --> 01:16:22,603
will realize its true power

1016
01:16:22,645 --> 01:16:23,839
So... So what?

1017
01:16:23,880 --> 01:16:26,815
So dad, Dragon and I
have been trained together

1018
01:16:26,849 --> 01:16:29,613
If you join us, we're sure
to beat White Eyebrows

1019
01:16:29,652 --> 01:16:31,085
You're crazy!

1020
01:16:31,120 --> 01:16:34,021
