1021
01:16:34,056 --> 01:16:36,286
How do I have the time to fight?

1022
01:16:36,325 --> 01:16:37,349
I know

1023
01:16:37,393 --> 01:16:40,191
But without you, we won't have
two pairs of Pure Hearts

1024
01:16:40,229 --> 01:16:42,754
Forget it. You won't get
anything from Mrs. Scrooge

1025
01:16:42,799 --> 01:16:43,493
Let's go!

1026
01:16:44,000 --> 01:16:47,458
I'm still better than
a bankrupt man like you

1027
01:16:48,938 --> 01:16:50,496
Look at the animosity between you two?

1028
01:16:50,540 --> 01:16:52,940
How can you be a pair of Pure Hearts?

1029
01:16:52,975 --> 01:16:54,840
Forget it. Off we march to our deaths

1030
01:17:04,287 --> 01:17:06,448
OK. Just put it here

1031
01:17:14,096 --> 01:17:17,031
