1033
01:17:21,304 --> 01:17:23,272
perhaps maybe I'd agree

1034
01:17:24,974 --> 01:17:28,967
Rouge, I thought you loved Dragon

1035
01:17:29,011 --> 01:17:30,808
I used to think so too

1036
01:17:31,981 --> 01:17:33,812
But it turns out you love me

1037
01:17:35,751 --> 01:17:39,551
Before, I thought
I was destined for Dragon

1038
01:17:39,589 --> 01:17:40,920
