1041
01:17:46,963 --> 01:17:48,225
How beautiful!

1042
01:17:50,566 --> 01:17:52,500
Please come with us, Ms. Lam

1043
01:17:52,535 --> 01:17:53,900
Who are you?

1044
01:17:53,936 --> 01:17:56,234
Anyone running around
dressed like that has to be crazy

1045
01:17:56,272 --> 01:17:57,762
Take this. I will protect you

1046
01:17:57,807 --> 01:17:59,138
No need!

1047
01:18:05,948 --> 01:18:08,109
They're the people who wanna kill Dragon!

1048
01:18:08,150 --> 01:18:10,243
