1058
01:19:22,625 --> 01:19:24,388
60 times? I only see 2 wounds

1059
01:19:24,427 --> 01:19:26,224
They're very accurate

1060
01:19:26,262 --> 01:19:28,423
Each time they stabbed the same place

1061
01:19:29,832 --> 01:19:32,858
So you're the one What?

1062
01:19:32,902 --> 01:19:34,597
The one I'm destined for

1063
01:19:35,471 --> 01:19:36,460
Go Kiddie Kim

1064
01:19:36,505 --> 01:19:38,097
Tell my mom to save me!

1065
01:19:38,140 --> 01:19:41,166
Don't worry, Rouge! My mom, your mom...

1066
01:19:41,210 --> 01:19:42,939
Every mom everywhere
I'll get them all to save you

1067
01:19:42,979 --> 01:19:44,810
Don't worry...

1068
01:19:44,847 --> 01:19:46,781
How can you be so heartless?

1069
01:19:46,816 --> 01:19:48,841
Can't you take the knives out
when you leave!

1070
01:19:50,853 --> 01:19:55,347
Jenny, I've just
brought your daughter here

1071
01:19:57,026 --> 01:19:57,754
What did you say?

1072
01:19:58,327 --> 01:20:01,888
I give you an hour
to bring Lincoln Lam here

1073
01:20:10,606 --> 01:20:12,039
That was Boss White, wasn't it?

1074
01:20:16,012 --> 01:20:18,674
I had a private detective follow you

1075
01:20:18,714 --> 01:20:20,682
Boss White's not an ordinary man

1076
01:20:20,716 --> 01:20:22,581
And I know you two had a relationship

1077
01:20:24,754 --> 01:20:28,315
Honey, forgive me

1078
01:20:28,357 --> 01:20:31,019
What ever happened before our marriage
doesn't matter

1079
01:20:31,060 --> 01:20:32,925
He's forcing you to attack me, isn't he?

1080
01:20:34,230 --> 01:20:35,925
They've kidnapped Rouge

1081
01:20:36,165 --> 01:20:37,792
Take me to him

1082
01:20:37,833 --> 01:20:41,234
No. If you go, he'll kill you

1083
01:20:41,270 --> 01:20:43,067
Some disasters can't be prevented

1084
01:20:44,540 --> 01:20:47,031
Rouge is not my real daughter

1085
01:20:47,076 --> 01:20:50,273
but I love her like one

1086
01:20:52,915 --> 01:20:54,041
Honey

1087
01:21:03,726 --> 01:21:07,560
Boss Lam, you've got
a real leader's courage

1088
01:21:07,596 --> 01:21:08,995
You do everything yourself

1089
01:21:09,031 --> 01:21:13,127
Truly a man capable of great things

1090
01:21:13,169 --> 01:21:17,367
Jenny, have you told him what I want?

1091
01:21:18,774 --> 01:21:21,470
I'm willing to give you all my wealth

1092
01:21:21,510 --> 01:21:23,410
But you must set my daughter free

1093
01:21:23,446 --> 01:21:25,971
Then we'll leave right away

1094
01:21:26,015 --> 01:21:27,642
Give him the contract

1095
01:21:38,294 --> 01:21:39,158
(Eat shit!)

1096
01:21:41,130 --> 01:21:43,223
Don't worry, boss. Go save Rouge

1097
01:21:43,265 --> 01:21:44,163
Come on

1098
01:21:44,934 --> 01:21:47,164
So the losers come back to tempt death?

1099
01:21:49,138 --> 01:21:50,070
Kill them!

1100
01:22:38,187 --> 01:22:43,682
Principal of the Academy has taught you
the Technique of the Pure and Lethal Heart

1101
01:22:43,726 --> 01:22:45,717
So your Pure Heart must be the bird?

1102
01:22:45,761 --> 01:22:47,888
Mind your own business! Hawk!

1103
01:22:52,868 --> 01:22:54,335
You're a total embarrassment!

1104
01:23:33,275 --> 01:23:34,537
Get behind me!

1105
01:23:47,089 --> 01:23:48,386
You came?

1106
01:23:48,424 --> 01:23:49,857
In a clutch, I stand by my family

1107
01:23:49,892 --> 01:23:51,052
Let's get him

1108
01:23:55,931 --> 01:23:56,920
Let's get him

1109
01:24:08,877 --> 01:24:09,775
Phoenix

1110
01:24:11,146 --> 01:24:16,174
Sorry, our timing never seems right

1111
01:24:16,218 --> 01:24:18,049
Because you've no feeling for me

1112
01:24:20,956 --> 01:24:25,893
It's all my fault. I forgot everything...

1113
01:25:09,905 --> 01:25:11,395
I remember

1114
01:25:13,676 --> 01:25:14,540
I remember

1115
01:25:15,878 --> 01:25:17,209
I remember! You saved me

1116
01:25:19,181 --> 01:25:20,273
You removed the poison

1117
01:25:21,517 --> 01:25:23,007
You took me to Mount Hua

1118
01:25:24,086 --> 01:25:25,280
Hawk went the wrong way

1119
01:25:27,690 --> 01:25:29,453
I recovered my memory...

1120
01:25:31,126 --> 01:25:32,457
Really?

1121
01:25:34,697 --> 01:25:37,165
Phoenix, this is no time for love

1122
01:25:37,266 --> 01:25:38,733
We can't hold up much longer

1123
01:25:38,767 --> 01:25:40,632
The pure of heart are invincible!

1124
01:25:40,669 --> 01:25:41,533
Let's not exaggerate too much

1125
01:25:43,339 --> 01:25:44,829
White Eyebrows is too strong

1126
01:25:44,873 --> 01:25:47,034
Working together with a single heart
so that we can defeat him...

1127
01:25:47,076 --> 01:25:48,441
Let's get that bastard...

1128
01:25:50,813 --> 01:25:52,872
The family that stays together
kicks ass together!

1129
01:25:52,915 --> 01:25:56,316
What tricks to you have left fight with?

1130
01:26:00,622 --> 01:26:01,418
Let's go!

1131
01:26:17,673 --> 01:26:18,469
Watch out!

1132
01:26:37,693 --> 01:26:39,126
Flying Swallow Attack!

1133
01:27:07,689 --> 01:27:09,816
One - Family - United - Always

1134
01:27:09,858 --> 01:27:11,155
Succeeds!

1135
01:27:20,202 --> 01:27:21,066
Father-in-law

1136
01:27:21,103 --> 01:27:23,003
Let cops handle him

1137
01:27:23,705 --> 01:27:25,605
I like the sound of father-in-law

1138
01:27:25,641 --> 01:27:26,903
What your say goes

1139
01:27:27,910 --> 01:27:29,878
How about me? Mother-in-law!

1140
01:27:30,846 --> 01:27:33,110
And me? Honey!

1141
01:27:41,390 --> 01:27:46,384
Dad, Mom...

1142
01:27:46,428 --> 01:27:48,123
I just saw 4 people

1143
01:27:48,163 --> 01:27:50,324
fly past the moon

1144
01:27:51,800 --> 01:27:53,631
You must have been dreaming

1145
01:27:53,669 --> 01:27:55,864
People can't fly!

1146
01:27:56,805 --> 01:27:59,239
You must be watching too much TV

1147
01:27:59,274 --> 01:28:01,367
What an over-active imagination!


